# Claude Code — devbox

This is a **disposable work devbox** — an LXC container on evilbot (Proxmox host at
192.168.1.145). Destroy and re-provision freely; nothing here is permanent.

Work repos live in `~/work/`. Each is an independent project; see per-repo notes below.

> Copy this file to `CLAUDE.md.template` and fill in your own project details.
> `CLAUDE.md.template` is gitignored — it documents private work repos and internal
> architecture, so it must never be committed. Only this sanitized example is public.

## Homelab Access

| Host | IP | Access |
|---|---|---|
| evilbot (Proxmox) | 192.168.1.145 | `ssh root@192.168.1.145` |
| claudebot (AI sandbox) | 192.168.1.222 | `ssh root@192.168.1.222` |

GitHub SSH key is pre-installed at `~/.ssh/work_id_ed25519` and routed through
`~/.ssh/config` — `git clone git@github.com:...` works out of the box.

